That would be Dmatix's SCP-1710 , which was on my mind throughout this as well.

Though the last log was cute as all hell, I really couldn't get into this. This whole shtick is something that's already played out for me, and it's not helped by how bare and generic the more Eldritch of the pair comes off as.

It's pretty adorable for it to be taking the cactus under its wing, it's certainly humorous, but the whole thing leading up to it felt really insubstantial, making this a little disappointing for me.







